'''Flangth''' was a kind of [[Foodstuff/Legends|food]]. It was the primary offering of the [[Flangth-2-Go]] restaurant chain,<ref name="HSSB">''[[Han Solo and the Corporate Sector Sourcebook]]''</ref> and one of the dishes available in the mess at the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] base on [[Arbra/Legends|Arbra]].<ref name="SW62">[[Star Wars (1977) 62|''Star Wars'' (1977) 62]]</ref> Young [[Klaus Vandangante/Legends|Klaus Vandangante]] found flangth to be rather unpalatable.<ref name="HSSB" />

During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], a group of [[Privateer/Legends|privateers]] from the ''[[Far Orbit]]'' were to meet an [[Agent/Legends|agent]] of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] at [[Lean Nuuti Bar and Grill]] on [[StarForge Station]]. The group were to identify themselves to the [[Unidentified Ithorian (StarForge Station)|agent]] by ordering flangth and [[ootoowerg]]s with [[Shasa ale]].<ref name="PW">{{WEGCite|book=The Far Orbit Project|story=Preparing for War}}</ref>

